                "@type": "Person",
                "name": "Justin Time"
            },
            "reviewBody": "A true recipe with no cheating. You don't need sugar, you just need time. Someone looked at all the misleading cooking times, experimented and concluded that there is no way you can get caramelized onions in less than 45 min.\n\n\nI agree with John from the comments, a perfect recipe."
